The Arquillian team is proud to announce the 2.0.1.Final release of the Graphene component! This release is focused on browser interoperability and bug fixes;
Pëtr Andreev fixed request guards in Internet Explorer <= 9 Jiří Locker fixed tests to work on Safari Juraj Huska addressed a flaw in @InFrame functionality
